entry.title: New release for Nautical Backup: v2.14.0
entry.content:
What's Changed

Maybe breaking?

  • Fix rsync exclude by @Minituff in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/523
    • This merge technically does change the way the arguments are parsed as part of the rsync command. While this does fix the issue https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/issues/496 it may have unintended changes if you made workarounds to this.
    • Due to this change being a bug fix and not a new feature-set or API change I am not bumping the version to 3.0

Everything else

  • Update minituff/nautical-backup Docker tag to v2.13.10 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/520
  • Update dependency mkdocs-material to v9.6.16 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/521
  • Update ncipollo/release-action action to v1.18.0 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/511
  • Update docker/metadata-action action to v5.8.0 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/522
  • Update docker/login-action action to v3.5.0 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/pull/524

Full Changelog: https://github.com/Minituff/nautical-backup/compare/v2.13.10...v2.14.0
